@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8080
@json = application/json
@taskId = task-tracking-optical-closure-0021

### Tracking optical linkage closure test
### Goal:
### 1) verify patrol waypoints are reported to planning module for feasibility check before target is available
### 2) verify tracking dispatch -> simulate ownship arrival -> emit optical DDS command

### 1. Reset local mock state
POST {{baseUrl}}/mock/dds/reset

### 2. Set ownship initial state
POST {{baseUrl}}/mock/dds/navigation
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "platform_id": 1001,
  "speed_mps": 6.2,
  "heading_deg": 90.0,
  "longitude": 121.5000000,
  "latitude": 31.220000,
  "timestamp": "2026-03-24T10:00:00Z"
}

### 3. Create tracking task with optical linkage enabled
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tasks
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "task_id": "{{taskId}}",
  "task_type": "escort",
  "task_name": "tracking-optical-closure-test",
  "task_source": "planning_service",
  "priority": 1,
  "target_info": {
    "target_id": "target-closure-001",
    "target_batch_no": 201,
    "target_type_code": 106,
    "threat_level": 2,
    "target_name": "target-closure-001",
    "military_civil_attr": 1
  },
  "task_area": {
    "area_type": "polygon",
    "points": [
      { "longitude": 121.49, "latitude": 31.21 },
      { "longitude": 121.52, "latitude": 31.21 },
      { "longitude": 121.52, "latitude": 31.23 },
      { "longitude": 121.49, "latitude": 31.23 }
    ]
  },
  "expected_speed": 12.0,
  "update_interval_sec": 1,
  "end_condition": {
    "duration_sec": 300,
    "out_of_region_finish": true
  },
  "linkage_param": {
    "enable_optical": true,
    "enable_evidence": true
  }
}

### 4. Inspect planning plan reports
### Expect at least one item with plan_type = patrol (patrol waypoints sent to planning module)
GET {{baseUrl}}/mock/collaboration/planning/plans

### 5. Simulate planning feasibility callback for the reported patrol route
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tasks/callbacks/planning/feasibility
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "task_id": "{{taskId}}",
  "plan_type": "patrol",
  "feasible": true,
  "reason": "route accepted by planning",
  "suggested_action": "continue",
  "callback_time": "2026-03-24T10:00:05Z"
}

### 6. Inspect current task result before target input
### Expect task_status waiting_target, patrol_plan_output populated, planning_callback received
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tasks/{{taskId}}/result

### 7. Set target perception input
POST {{baseUrl}}/mock/dds/perception
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "target_count": 1,
  "targets": [
    {
      "source_platform_id": 2001,
      "target_id": "target-closure-001",
      "target_batch_no": 201,
      "target_bearing_deg": 35.0,
      "target_distance_m": 3000,
      "target_absolute_speed_mps": 6.2,
      "target_absolute_heading_deg": 90.0,
      "target_longitude": 121.5030000,
      "target_latitude": 31.2200000,
      "target_type_code": 106,
      "military_civil_attr": 1,
      "target_name": "target-closure-001",
      "threat_level": 2,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-24T10:00:00Z",
      "active": true
    }
  ]
}

### 8. Inspect generated tracking dispatch
GET {{baseUrl}}/mock/autonomy/tracking/logs

### 10. Inspect current task result before manual arrival
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tasks/{{taskId}}/result

### 11. Inspect current local situation
GET {{baseUrl}}/mock/dds/situation

### 12. Manually simulate ownship arrival near the dispatched tracking point
### Replace longitude latitude heading_deg speed_mps with the dispatched point values you want to verify
POST {{baseUrl}}/mock/dds/navigation
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "platform_id": 1001,
  "speed_mps": 6.2,
  "heading_deg": 90.0,
  "longitude": 121.49984516225155,
  "latitude": 31.21999996149976,
  "timestamp": "2026-03-24T10:02:00Z"
}

### 13. Inspect local situation after manual arrival
GET {{baseUrl}}/mock/dds/situation

### 14. Inspect emitted optical DDS commands
GET {{baseUrl}}/mock/collaboration/optical-linkage/commands

### 15. Inspect media stream access logs
GET {{baseUrl}}/mock/collaboration/media/stream-access

### 16. Inspect task result after manual arrival
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tasks/{{taskId}}/result

### 17. Cleanup task
POST {{baseUrl}}/mock/dds/navigation
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "platform_id": 1001,
  "speed_mps": 6.2,
  "heading_deg": 90.0,
  "longitude": 122.49,
  "latitude": 32.21,
  "timestamp": "2026-03-24T10:02:00Z"
}

### 18. Cleanup task
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tasks/{{taskId}}/terminate
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "reason": "cleanup"
}


